reviews.title: Very disappointed.
reviews.comment: Ever since I updated this, you guys ripped out my user defined settings (personal background, ongoing/outgoing font colors etc). I even had my user defined settings backed up on my SD and I it\'s not restoring it when I click on it.. So now my background is just normal. The reason why downloaded this app in the first place was because I could customize it. But now it won\'t even save my customizations. So disappointed in go sms!!! Won\'t rate 5 stars until its fixed. ):

reviews.title: GREAT SMS APP BUT TOO EASY TO BYPASS
reviews.comment: I really love this app except its weak security. I CAN EASILY BYPASS BOTH NUMBER LOCK AND PARTERN LOCK JUST BY USING ROOT EXPLORER AND DELETING SOME FILE IN DATA FOLDER OF GO SMS. Please fix this irritating bug. I will very pleased to give it 5 stars. On the whole, it is still the best sms app on play store

reviews.comment: So glad we finally have all the emojis. Cool backgrounds, fun conversations. I was waiting to rate this app. First time ever rating an app. Keep up the good work. I recently had to replace my S3 and had to buy my background again and lost my other ones. There should be a recovery option for those who get new devices. After the last update it\'s a glitch after you first up open the app. It\'s s blank white screen with go sms logo bar at the top. Fix it. Until then 3 stars instead of 5.
